{"tid":1436382,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[香城online] 大埔關卡危險地區","createTime":"2019-08-09T09:36:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T11:34:01.000Z","uid":183601,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1b1f77d21a0abe9cdb35aa3271c6661acee22f4a","tid":1436382,"uid":183601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:36:38.000Z","msg":"各位玩家都知聽日隻game會開啟大埔關卡<br />\n先唔理系統嘅不反對通知書上訴成功與否<br />\n對於一啲大埔或其他區嘅玩家<br />\n有個地方一定要高度留意<br />\n就係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大埔頭</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/isOx5n6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FisOx5n6.png&h=52590e62&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n先睇睇呢張圖<br />\n藍圈為大埔頭巴士總站+太湖範圍<br />\n紅線為原訂遊行路線<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>大埔頭巴士站</strong></span>絕對係危險地方<br />\n<br />\n由於現時大埔關卡不獲發不反對通知書<br />\n如果玩家在大埔頭巴士站聚集就有可能被系統視為非法集結<br />\n<br />\n先講講區外玩家可以點去大埔頭巴士站<br />\n1、搭E41直到總站<br />\n除非由機場/東涌過來，否則一般玩家不會使用<br />\n2、太和站步行<br />\n太和只有一條路去大埔頭巴士站<br />\n汀太路轉入大埔頭路<br />\n（要經過泳池/運動場附近路口）<br />\n沿途更會穿過行人隧道<br />\n<br />\n離開大埔頭巴士站既路極少<br />\n睇睇下面呢張圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Fxrqh9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Fxrqh9.jpg&h=30e33958&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1、返回太和站（橙色線）<br />\n沿大埔頭路行返出去汀太路<br />\n（要經過泳池/運動場附近路口）<br />\n2、去富亨<br />\n有兩個方法<br />\na. 網球場附近小路<br />\nb. 正常玩家會沿大埔頭路行返出去汀太路（線色線）<br />\n（要經過泳池/運動場附近路口）<br />\n3、經隧道橫過汀太路往大埔中心方向（藍色線）<br />\n（要經過泳池/運動場附近路口）<br />\n<br />\n亦即絕大部分離開路線必經泳池/運動場附近路口<br />\n<br />\n該路口只要有二三十隻怪<br />\n就可以<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>完全包圍</strong></span>大埔頭巴士站<br />\n唯一生機就係走入大埔頭村屋去三育中學方向<br />\n或走入太湖花園 (屋苑一期正門平時無閘, 得更亭, 非住客自由出入係無人知)<br />\n<br />\n反而<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>風水廣場</strong></span>球場比較方便集合 (第一張圖橙色圓點)<br />\n詳情可參閱早幾日既活動<br />\n風水廣場位於大埔市中心<br />\n毗鄰大埔中心巴士總站, 商場, 大元邨<br />\n多路入多路走, 易入易散<br />\n加上有上次集會經驗, 又係原定遊行路線會經過之處<br />\n故此,<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">玩家唔去大埔頭, 喺風水踢下波玩下先, 再觀察下怪嘅動向會唔會較好?</span><br />\n<br />\n另外, 我對路線尾段嘅<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">廣福道</span></strong></span>都有啲睇法<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SK9UziU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSK9UziU.png&h=a509de77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">廣福道</span></strong>為預計打怪戰場<br />\n上圖可見附近大量唐樓, 好易比啲怪預先喺制高點佈防安排槍手<br />\n加上大埔墟無大型屋苑同商場做支援, 無論區內外玩家都好難安全撤離, 好易被怪圍<br />\n<br />\n仲有, 運輸處封路有機會配合怪出動<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">水炮車</span></strong> <br />\n個人認為<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">廣福道</span></strong>同<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大埔太和路(即一田對出)</span></strong>都非常適合<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">水炮車</span></strong>出擊<br />\n<br />\n歡迎多啲大埔玩家分析<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5c836536ede941292b51a29092161d0f2d8e0b1","tid":1436382,"uid":127991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:42:29.000Z","msg":"廣福道右邊就係寶湖商場駁住超級成其實還可以 不過唔知會唔會有狗block條路"},{"pid":"b7400d8d17f148fd675692210aa76935c704509e","tid":1436382,"uid":33325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:56:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中聯辦策劃元朗恐襲事件，唔可以比佢沉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家入去大大力推 <br />\n[整合] 葉虎門資料整合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1382583\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1382583</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />請巴絲bookmark後定時推上頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ceb4a2df48ccfcceb25b66d4731b131f02da4d4","tid":1436382,"uid":34661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:57:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"f9cc8835a2c88f18229ec0e089adf5e8c6e07966","tid":1436382,"uid":210140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:26:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cb0ad60d8f349371d8a436e4f7640e364c6ba7b6","tid":1436382,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:34:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}